---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import MenuButton from '../components/MenuButton.astro';
import ScrollToggle from '../components/ScrollToggle.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={"OtterlyOmari | About"} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		
		<main id="content">
			<div id="home-section">
				<a href="/" aria-label="Home">
					<img src="/logo.png"  class="image" alt="Omari Tidemere" width="1372" height="213" />
				</a>

				<h5 class="t-outline no-pointer">the cute motherfluffer your mom warned you about</h5>

				<div id="container">
					<section id="section">
						<h3 class="t-outline about-text">About me</h3>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">Hi there! It's me, your friendly neighborhood otter, Omari</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I'd like to thank you for taking the time to look at my website!</p>  
						<p class="t-outline about-text">Now that you're here, I'd like to tell you a bit about myself</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I'm Omari Allyn Tidemere A fluffy sea otter on the internet who likes to help others and spread joy,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">if I can make as much as one person happy then  I'll be happy too. the smiles on others faces motivate me to keep going</p>	
					    <p class="t-outline about-text">It's a reminder to me that no matter how hard things get, it's worth living life to the fullest.</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I absolutely love exploring nature, telling stories, whether it's a poem, a sonnet, a full-length novel, or even a video game.</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I'm also a music producer, and you can find my works <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@symphonyoftidemereyt/" style="color: lime;" class="no-deco">here</a>!</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">my discography is varied, spanning multiple genres and styles, sometimes its covers, other times original compositions, I hope you enjoy them!</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">And of course, as you may already know, I make content over on YouTube!</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">Aimed at a diverse audience of furries and non-furries alike, my content is PG-13 at best,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">meaning there's no profanity, nor any raunchy stuff that's inappropriate for minors.</p>
		
						<h5 class="t-outline about-text-2" >🦦 Some Fun Facts About Me!</h5>
						<p class="t-outline about-text"> - I am a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therian_subculture" style="color: lime;" class="no-deco">Therian (ΘΔ)</a> ! </p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text"> - I am an avid gamer and reader!</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text"> (My favorite book at the moment is <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/61439040-1984" style="color: lime;" class="no-deco">1984 by George Orwell</a>!)</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">- I wrote my first novel, "Shadows of Gaia: The Rise of Zenith" in 2024, you can <a href="/library" style="color: lime;" class="no-deco">read a sample now</a>!</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text"> - I overcame severe mental health issues thanks to furries!</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text"> - I'm shy but also affectionate in real life just as I am online!</p>
	
						<h5 class="t-outline about-text" style="color: yellow;">⚠️ Please leave my pages if you are a cyberbully!</h5>

						<h5 class="t-outline about-text">DNI (Do Not Interact) if you are...</h5>

						<p class="t-outline about-text">⛔ A bigot of any kind</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">⛔ An unethical paraphile (zoo, pedo or necro)</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">⛔ A drama addicted and/or narcissistic person</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">⛔ A Zionist, Neo Nazi, or other extremist</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">⛔ Someone who engages in harassment or hate speech</p>

						<p class="t-outline about-text">In addition, I strongly prefer that only respectful and kind individuals interact with my content,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">and I reserve the right to block or report anyone who engages in harassment, hate speech, or any form of toxic behavior.</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I want this space to be a positive and inclusive environment for everyone.</p>
	
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I want to create a welcoming and inclusive space for everyone,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">and I hope that you can be a part of that! that being said,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I do prefer that only adults interact with me in direct messages, as I have had some bad experiences with kids in the past,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">and I want to avoid any potential issues. </p>
						
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I also want to make it clear that I do not condone or support any form of illegal or unethical behavior, </p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">and I reserve the right to block or report anyone who engages in such behavior,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">and furthermore, I do not hate children, I just prefer to keep my interactions with them limited and supervised (public) for their safety and mine</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">for the time being- I'm open to changing this policy in the future as I grow and learn, but for now,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">I want to prioritize the safety and well-being of everyone involved.</p>
							

						<p class="t-outline about-text">I don't wish to have any sort of negativity in my space,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">and I hope you can understand that as I wish to foster</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">a positive, kind and caring community! Let's uplift one another,</p>
						<p class="t-outline about-text">help each other and never bring others down. Help each others lights shine bright like the stars!</p>

						<div class="contact-buttons">
							<MenuButton href="mailto:omari@otterlyomari.com" label="✉️ Email" />
							<MenuButton href="https://t.me/OtterlyOmari" label="📱 Telegram" />
							<MenuButton href="https://discord.com/users/123456789012345678" label="💬 Discord DM" />
						</div>

						<h5 class="t-outline about-text" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">
							💛 I try to respond within 2-3 days. Please be patient with me!
						</h5>

						<p class="t-outline about-text">Anyway, I don't want to stretch this too much longer so, have an amazing day, I love you all!</p>

						<p class="t-outline about-text">~ Omari Allyn Tidemere</p>
					</section>
				</div>
				


				<MenuButton href="/" data-astro-prefetch label="Go Back" />

		</main>
		<Footer/>

		<ScrollToggle />

		<style>
			main {
				backdrop-filter: blur(0.4rem);
				z-index: 9999;
				background-color: transparent;
			}

			.contact-buttons {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 1rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
			}

			#section {
				width: 100%; /* Adjust as needed */
				margin: 0 auto;
				backdrop-filter: blur(0.6rem);
				background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1rem;
				will-change: transform, opacity;
				transform: translateZ(0);
			}


			.about-text, h5:hover, h3:hover, h2:hover, h1:hover {
				text-align: center;
				color: white;
			}

			.about-text        { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
			.about-text + h5   { margin-top: 2rem; }

			.about-text-2 {
				text-align: center;
			}

			#container {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: flex-start;
				padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
				backdrop-filter: blur(0.4rem);
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {

				/* prevent edge-to-edge compression feeling */
				#container {
					padding: 1.2rem 0.8rem 3rem;
					flex-direction: column;
				}

				/* improve readability on small screens */
				#section {
					width: 100%;
					padding: 0.5rem;
					backdrop-filter: blur(0.3rem);
				}
			}

			.no-pointer {
				pointer-events: none;
				transform: translateX(1.5rem);
			}
			
			h1,
			h2,
			h3,
			h4,
			h5,
			h6 {
				margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
				color: white;
				line-height: 1.2;
				font-family: 'Pulang', sans-serif;
			}
		</style>
	</body>

</html>
